name: 3326 Ride for charity:water
description:
Get onboard and help support the crew on the 3326 Ride - http://33-26.com/.

We are proudly supporting them with a limited edition print available now until 30 December. There are 75 prints in total!

Veloposters are donating a portion of all prints sold to the campaign.

A 1 of 1 print is also up for auction with all proceeds going to charity:water
------------------------------------------------------------

THIS IS A PRE ORDER ONLY!
Available until Dec 30th.

Prints will then be sent out early in the new year. I am a one man show, so please be patient with me - i'll do my utmost to get these out to you quickly.

------------------------------------------------------------

Giclée print 
270gsm Smoothe white archival paper 
A3+ (330mm x 482mm) or 13" x 19". 
Limited to 75 prints

There is approx 20mm(+-) left inside the edge of the sheet for matting, effectively giving you an A3 image area. 

Each print is hand signed and numbered. 
They look great mounted and framed.

Sold as prints only. These are unframed.

Top image shows print 
Bottom image is the detail

Prints fit into the 40x50cm Ribba Frames from Ikea. 
Note: You will lose some of the top under the matting in the Ribba frame.
